498
00:38:27,779 --> 00:38:30,111
I don't think he's a spirit guide.

499
00:38:31,241 --> 00:38:34,028
The alebrijes of this world
can take many forms.

500
00:38:34,118 --> 00:38:37,076
They are as mysterious
as they are powerful.

501
00:38:42,961 --> 00:38:46,453
Or maybe he's just a dog.
Come, I need your eyes.

502
00:38:48,091 --> 00:38:51,675
You are the audience. Darkness.

503
00:38:52,303 --> 00:38:56,171
And from the darkness, a giant papaya.

504
00:38:57,517 --> 00:39:03,638
Dancers emerge from the papaya,
and the dancers are all me.

505
00:39:04,566 --> 00:39:08,309
And they go to drink from the milk
of their mother, who is a cactus.

506
00:39:08,528 --> 00:39:14,194
But who is also me.
And her milk is not milk but tears.

507
00:39:15,535 --> 00:39:16,615
Is it too obvious?

508
00:39:16,744 --> 00:39:20,157
I think it's just
the right amount of obvious?

509
00:39:20,331 --> 00:39:23,539
It could use some music.
Oh, what if you did like...

510
00:39:27,171 --> 00:39:28,502
Oh! And then it could go...

511
00:39:34,220 --> 00:39:36,176
