512
00:39:37,015 --> 00:39:39,051
Yes! Fire! Everywhere!

513
00:39:39,309 --> 00:39:43,473
Inspired!
You have the spirit of an artist.

514
00:39:45,398 --> 00:39:48,140
The dancers exit.
The music fades, the lights go out.

515
00:39:48,318 --> 00:39:51,526
And Ernesto de la Cruz
rises to the stage!

516
00:39:55,617 --> 00:39:56,652
