00:42:11,169 --> 00:42:12,033
We're almost there.

554
00:42:17,383 --> 00:42:18,714
Keep up, chamaco. Come on.

555
00:42:27,685 --> 00:42:32,179
-Cousin Héctor!
-Hey! These guys! Hey, Tio!

