580
00:44:06,617 --> 00:44:10,280
No. You know I don't play anymore,
Cheech. The guitar is for the kid.

581
00:44:10,913 --> 00:44:14,280
You want it, you got to earn it.

582
00:44:16,127 --> 00:44:18,618
Ay, only for you, amigo.

583
00:44:21,465 --> 00:44:22,796
An)’ requests?

