00:48:06,107 --> 00:48:08,473
It's a battle of the bands, amigos.

621
00:48:08,859 --> 00:48:13,853
The winner gets to play for the maestro
himself, Ernesto de la Cruz...

622
00:48:14,031 --> 00:48:16,363
at his ﬁesta tonight!

