00:50:26,497 --> 00:50:28,158
Oh, come on, kid.

653
00:50:39,009 --> 00:50:40,749
De la Cruzcito, you're on now!

654
00:50:40,844 --> 00:50:44,587
Miguel, look at me. Hey, look at me.
You can do this.

655
00:50:44,682 --> 00:50:46,513
Grab their attention and don't let it go.

656
00:50:47,101 --> 00:50:49,183
Make them listen, chamaco.
You've got this.

657
00:50:49,353 --> 00:50:51,469
De la Cruzcito!

658
00:51:00,364 --> 00:51:02,355
What's he doing? Why isn't he playing?

659
00:51:03,117 --> 00:51:05,358
Bring back the singing dogs!

660
00:51:17,131 --> 00:51:19,918
Que bien! Vamonos! Whoo!

661
00:51:28,017 --> 00:51:31,509
