821
01:04:57,492 --> 01:05:00,575
That's crazy!
De la Cruz wrote all his own songs.

822
01:05:00,954 --> 01:05:02,819
You want to tell him or should I?

823
01:05:02,956 --> 01:05:08,701
Héctor, I never meant to take credit.
We made a great team, but you died...

824
01:05:08,795 --> 01:05:13,710
and I only sang your songs because
I wanted to keep a part of you alive.

825
01:05:13,883 --> 01:05:15,339
How generous!

826
01:05:15,510 --> 01:05:17,626
You really did play together.

827
01:05:17,804 --> 01:05:21,843
I don't want to fight about it.
Ijust want you to make it right.

828
01:05:22,016 --> 01:05:25,679
Miguel can put my photo up,
and I can cross over the bridge.

829
01:05:26,479 --> 01:05:31,269
I can see my girl.
Ernesto, remember the night I left?

830
01:05:31,401 --> 01:05:32,766
That was a long time ago.

831
01:05:32,902 --> 01:05:36,235
We drank together and you told me
you would move Heaven and Earth...

832
01:05:36,406 --> 01:05:40,194
for your amigo.
