we're this close to reaching our dream?

845
01:06:22,285 --> 01:06:24,116
This was your dream. You'll manage.

846
01:06:24,245 --> 01:06:25,951
I can't do this
without your songs, Héctor.

847
01:06:26,080 --> 01:06:29,743
