852
01:06:58,404 --> 01:06:59,985
I thought
it must have been something I ate.

853
01:07:00,156 --> 01:07:01,987
Perhaps it was that chorizo, my friend.

854
01:07:02,659 --> 01:07:04,866
Or something I drank.

855
01:07:08,498 --> 01:07:10,238
I woke up dead.

856
01:07:12,168 --> 01:07:14,329
You poisoned me.

857
01:07:14,504 --> 01:07:17,746
You're confusing movies
with reality, Héctor.

858
01:07:17,924 --> 01:07:21,166
All this time,
I thought it was just bad luck.

859
01:07:22,595 --> 01:07:24,506
