on their stupid ofrenda.

888
01:10:08,636 --> 01:10:11,378
Hey, chamaco. It's okay. It's okay.

889
01:10:11,514 --> 01:10:13,971
Itold them I didn't care.

890
01:10:18,020 --> 01:10:20,853
Héctor! Héctor?

891
01:10:21,899 --> 01:10:24,515
