you wanted to cross the bridge.

894
01:10:35,621 --> 01:10:41,036
I just wanted to see her again.
I never should have left Santa Cecilia.

895
01:10:42,670 --> 01:10:44,501
I wish I could apologize.

896
01:10:44,881 --> 01:10:47,873
