her papa was trying to come home.

897
01:10:48,885 --> 01:10:51,001
That he loved her so much.

898
01:10:53,389 --> 01:10:54,799
My Coco...

899
01:10:57,560 --> 01:10:58,970
Coco?

900
01:11:15,495 --> 01:11:17,531
