That she'd miss me.

905
01:11:50,947 --> 01:11:54,610
Maybe put up my photo.
But it never happened.

906
01:11:55,952 --> 01:11:57,237
You know the worst part?

907
01:11:57,787 --> 01:12:00,449
Even if I never got to see Coco
in the living world...

908
01:12:00,623 --> 01:12:05,538
